  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pawn Shop: Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of \"<strong>Pawn Shop: Simulator</strong>\" – a unique game where you step into the shoes of a pawn shop owner! Experience the thrill of negotiations, trading, and building your empire while uncovering the stories behind every item that lands on your counter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                Trade with customers and offer prices with profit in mind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/11e6bfe0ec62763c47b0834680b95548.poster.avif?t=1765397746\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/11e6bfe0ec62763c47b0834680b95548.webm?t=1765397746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/11e6bfe0ec62763c47b0834680b95548.mp4?t=1765397746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                        Participate in auctions to stock up your pawn shop inventory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/6a2882ad85fd3de5d38de869f2f3e413.poster.avif?t=1765397746\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/6a2882ad85fd3de5d38de869f2f3e413.webm?t=1765397746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/6a2882ad85fd3de5d38de869f2f3e413.mp4?t=1765397746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                           And through it all, watch out for the police...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/65af839cf0b4c33df67cbced05c7cd8a.poster.avif?t=1765397746\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/65af839cf0b4c33df67cbced05c7cd8a.webm?t=1765397746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3416530/extras/65af839cf0b4c33df67cbced05c7cd8a.mp4?t=1765397746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
